パズルメイとお絵かきメイと
by paste » Fri 02.26.2010 11:19 am おはよう~I was hoping someone might be able to help me with something: I bought the game in the title a loooong time ago, but now I've gotten to a puzzle that seems to have a bug in it. On the むずかしい difficulty level, puzzle 103 (in color), It seems like a have the right answer, but when I click the complete button, it says there's a mistake. Would anyone who speaks good japanese be able to help me search for information about this online? My japanese is a bit limited and the searches I did weren't very helpful.どうもありがとう！paste
