Re: パズルメイトお絵かきメイト
by Hyperworm » Sat 02.27.2010 2:53 pm Color picross, huh. It seems much more likely that you just made a single mistake on one of the rows and haven't spotted it... >_< Check, check, and check again. :/I tried Googling for puzzle solutions but couldn't find anything. :/The key word for this kind of search is normally 攻略.It means "capture" or "conquer" ("gain dominance over", "master").A 攻略法 is "a method for how to capture/master/conquer/beat something". 攻略本 and 攻略ガイド mean "strategy guide".A 攻略wiki is a basically a FAQ/walkthrough in wiki form.etc.It doesn't look like anyone's made one for that game, though.
fun translation snippets | need something translated?BTC@1KMZXgoWiDshQis5Z7feCx8jaiP4QAB2ks
