Re: パズルメイとお絵かきメイト
by paste » Sat 02.27.2010 5:39 pm Thanks Hyperworm.Unfortunately, I've checked and rechecked and it's correct in the rows but still telling me there's an error. That's only part of the problem, though. See, there's a mechanism in the game where if you tap on a square that is incorrect, it will put an X there for a second and won't fill it in with the color you are trying to enter. So there's a column in this particular puzzle I'm trying where the smallest number is 2. There's a piece colored in and I tap above it and it gives me the X. I tap below it and it gives me the X also. So there's definitely a problem in the puzzle.I was hoping maybe there was some kind of errata listed online, since this isn't the first puzzle in the game that's been incorrect, but I don't really know how to search for it I don't blame the developers, though, because there are a TON of puzzles in the cartridge so a couple with problems isn't so bad.Thank you for the help though!
